---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About SoniaBuddy"
  description="About SoniaBuddy, a West Bengal bus timetable, route finder and driver-included vehicle rental listing platform."
>
  <main class="legal-page">
    <section class="legal-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="eyebrow">West Bengal travel helper</p>
        <h1>About SoniaBuddy</h1>
        <p>
          SoniaBuddy helps people in West Bengal search bus timetable information, route finder results and driver-included rental vehicle listings from one simple website and app experience.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="legal-section">
      <div class="container legal-grid">
        <article class="legal-card">
          <h2>What SoniaBuddy does</h2>
          <p>
            SoniaBuddy is a local travel information and listing platform for West Bengal. Users can search bus routes, timetable pages, route finder results, and rental options such as car, bus, toto, auto, pickup van, ambulance, wedding bus, tour car and school bus listings.
          </p>
          <p>
            The goal is to make local travel planning easier for daily passengers, families, students, office users, tourists, vehicle owners and small businesses. We try to keep pages simple, mobile-friendly and useful for people who need quick travel information.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="legal-card">
          <h2>Bus timetable and route finder</h2>
          <p>
            SoniaBuddy provides bus route and timetable information for public convenience. Users can search source and destination names, view available routes, and explore route finder pages where direct or indirect travel options may be shown.
          </p>
          <p>
            Bus timing information can change because of traffic, weather, operator decisions, route changes, holidays or local conditions. Users should confirm important travel details before starting a journey.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="legal-card">
          <h2>Vehicle rental listings</h2>
          <p>
            SoniaBuddy also provides driver-included rental listing pages. Vehicle owners may add listings with vehicle type, model, photos, seats, service cities, purpose tags, price text, phone number and WhatsApp contact after accepting public contact consent.
          </p>
          <p>
            SoniaBuddy does not own the listed vehicles and does not operate as a transport company. Users contact the owner directly to confirm price, date, pickup point, timing, availability, route, driver details and final booking conditions.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="legal-card">
          <h2>For vehicle owners</h2>
          <p>
            Local vehicle owners can use SoniaBuddy to show their rental vehicle details to nearby users. Owners are responsible for entering correct information, keeping contact details active, uploading appropriate vehicle photos and updating availability when required.
          </p>
          <p>
            Listings may be reviewed, edited, rejected or removed if the information is fake, misleading, unsafe, duplicated, reported by users or not suitable for the platform.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="legal-card">
          <h2>Our role</h2>
          <p>
            SoniaBuddy is an information and discovery platform. We help connect users with route information and owner listings, but we do not guarantee bus availability, rental availability, final price, service quality, driver conduct or emergency response.
          </p>
          <p>
            Before booking any rental vehicle, users should call or message the owner and confirm the final rent, route, pickup time, waiting charge, toll, parking, night charge, driver allowance and vehicle condition.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="legal-card">
          <h2>Contact</h2>
          <p>
            For questions, correction requests, listing reports, privacy requests or business communication, please use our contact page.
          </p>
          <a class="legal-btn" href="/contact">Contact SoniaBuddy</a>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #eff8ff 0%, #ffffff 44%, #f8fbff 100%);
    color: #0f172a;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  .legal-hero {
    padding: 2.25rem 0 1rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e0f2fe 0%, #f8fbff 48%, #eef2ff 100%);
  }

  .legal-hero .container,
  .legal-section .container {
    max-width: 1040px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1rem;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex;
    margin: 0 0 0.65rem;
    padding: 0.28rem 0.65rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #dbeafe;
    color: #075985;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 900;
  }

  .legal-hero h1 {
    margin: 0 0 0.65rem;
    color: #0f172a;
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    line-height: 1.05;
  }

  .legal-hero p {
    max-width: 780px;
    margin: 0;
    color: #334155;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .legal-section {
    padding: 1rem 0 2.5rem;
  }

  .legal-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.85rem;
  }

  .legal-card {
    background: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid #dbeafe;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 1rem;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
  }

  .legal-card h2 {
    margin: 0 0 0.6rem;
    color: #0f172a;
    font-size: 1.18rem;
  }

  .legal-card p {
    margin: 0.45rem 0 0;
    color: #334155;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .legal-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    margin-top: 0.85rem;
    padding: 0.65rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #ff7a00;
    color: #ffffff;
    font-weight: 900;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  @media (min-width: 780px) {
    .legal-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }
  }
</style>
